description: Never duplicate database logic across layers
globs: apps/api/**
alwaysApply: false
---

# Database Logic

- All database access MUST go through repository classes in `api/modules/<domain>/repository.py`
- Services MUST NOT import SQLAlchemy query constructs directly
- Routers MUST NOT access the database or ORM models directly
- Use async SQLAlchemy sessions via dependency injection
